; Windows twin of the macOS/Linux raw-toxcore re-export surface.
;
; The account-export test fixture (toxee test/account_export/
; tox_profile_factory.dart) dlsym's a minimal raw toxcore API from the FFI
; library to fabricate real tox_profile savedata. ELF exports everything and
; the Mach-O export list re-exports these, but MSVC exports nothing from
; linked static libraries unless listed — so a default Windows build made the
; fixture fail with "The specified procedure could not be found"
; (tox_options_new), silently gutting ~19 account/export/password tests.
; Keep this list in sync with the fixture's lookups.
EXPORTS
    tox_options_new
    tox_options_default
    tox_options_free
    tox_new
    tox_kill
    tox_get_savedata_size
    tox_get_savedata
    tox_self_get_public_key
    tox_self_get_address
